Provides classes to support parallel and managed pages.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AugmentedElementAnnotations
    Class to work with fields in Page Objects.
    DefaultSeleniumElementLocator
    The default selenium element locator, which will lazily locate an element or an element list on a page.
    DefaultSeleniumElementLocatorFactory
    Default parallel element locator factory.
    DefaultSeleniumFieldDecorator
    Default Selenium decorator for use with WebPageFactory or PageFactory.
